    <string name="permission_content_privacy_agreement_full">无名杀App Privacy Policy and Disclaimer\n\nWe value your privacy. This app does not actively upload any stored information or collect personal identity information.\n\n1. Information Collection\n1.1 This app does not actively collect personal information.\n1.2 This app does not actively upload data to the network.\n1.3 All game data is saved locally.\n\n2. Local Data Usage\n2.1 Game settings are saved only on your device.\n2.2 All operations except updates and WebView usage are local.\n\n3. Permissions\nThis app may require:\n- Storage:&#160;Save/read game data\n- Network:&#160;Game updates and WebView content\n- Notification:&#160;Show update progress\n- Vibration:&#160;For WebView vibration API\n- Install:&#160;Update the app\n\n4. Data Security\n4.1 All data saved locally.\n4.2 Clear app data anytime.\n\n5. Disclaimer\nThis project does not provide complete HTML project files. Developers are not responsible for losses from imported HTML files.\nApps from unofficial sources may be modified. Developers are not responsible for losses from such apps.\n\n6. Contact\nQuestions? Visit project homepage:&#160;https://github.com/nonameShijian/noname-android-app</string>
